content: Celebrated the job offer with a rooftop dinner overlooking the city. But the real victory was seeing my algorithm perform well in live trading. Now, to integrate these lessons into my work at QuantFinance.

First day at QuantFinance. It's different from my previous role, but I'm here to learn and grow. And my trading algorithm? It's now part of my job, giving me a unique edge. Exciting times ahead in NYC.
